    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p><a href=\"http://nonprofitorgs.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/the-bird.jpg\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-11258\" alt=\"The-Bird\" src=\"http://nonprofitorgs.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/the-bird.jpg?w=300&#038;resize=300%2C176\" width=\"300\" height=\"176\" /></a>A long overdue follow up to my post on <a href=\"http://nonprofitorgs.wordpress.com/2009/10/19/29-nonprofit-bloggers-to-follow-on-twitter/\">29 Nonprofit Bloggers to Follow on Twitter</a>, below are 29 nonprofit resources that tweet regularly on subjects ranging from fundraising to social media to mobile communications. Of course, there are many other resources deserving of being listed &#8211; if you would like to add one, please do so in a comment below:</p>\n<hr />\n<table width=\"600\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"2\">\n<tbody>\n<tr valign=\"top\">\n<td height=\"76\"><strong>1.</strong></td>\n<td colspan=\"5\" align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" height=\"76\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.diosacommunications.com/nonprofitresources/Armchair%20Advocates.jpg?resize=73%2C73\" width=\"73\" height=\"73\" border=\"1\" /></td>\n<td height=\"76\"><strong>Armchair Advocates :: @</strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/ArmchrAdvocates\">ArmchrAdvocates</a><br />\nSocial Media, Cause Marketing, Nonprofit Tech<br />\n<a href=\"http://armchairadvocates.com/\">armchairadvocates.com</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr valign=\"top\">\n<td height=\"76\"><strong>2.</strong></td>\n<td colspan=\"5\" align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" height=\"76\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.diosacommunications.com/nonprofitresources/AFP.jpg?resize=73%2C73\" width=\"73\" height=\"73\" border=\"1\" /></td>\n<td height=\"76\"><strong>Association of Fundraising Professionals :: @</strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/afpihq\">AFPIHQ</a><br />\nFundraising, Research, Philanthropy<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.afpnet.org/\">afpnet.org</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr valign=\"top\">\n<td width=\"26\" height=\"76\"><strong>3.</strong></td>\n<td colspan=\"5\" align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" height=\"76\">\n<div><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.diosacommunications.com/nonprofitresources/Blackbaud.jpg?resize=73%2C73\" width=\"73\" height=\"73\" border=\"1\" /></div>\n</td>\n<td width=\"491\" height=\"76\"><strong>Blackbaud :: @</strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/blackbaud\">Blackbaud</a><a href=\"http://mobileactive.org/blog/katrinverclas\"><br />\n</a>Fundraising, Nonprofit Tecnology, News<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.blackbaud.com/\">blackbaud.com</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr valign=\"top\">\n<td height=\"76\"><strong>4.</strong></td>\n<td colspan=\"5\" align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" height=\"76\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.diosacommunications.com/nonprofitresources/charityvillage.jpg?resize=73%2C73\" width=\"73\" height=\"73\" border=\"1\" /></td>\n<td height=\"76\"><strong>Charity Village :: @</strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/charityvillage\">CharityVillage</a><a href=\"http://mobileactive.org/blog/katrinverclas\"><br />\n</a>News, Jobs, Fundraising, Canada<br />\n<a href=\"https://charityvillage.com/\">charityvillage.com</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr valign=\"top\">\n<td height=\"76\"><strong>5.</strong></td>\n<td colspan=\"5\" align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" height=\"76\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.diosacommunications.com/nonprofitresources/CharityNavigator.gif?resize=73%2C73\" width=\"73\" height=\"73\" border=\"1\" /></td>\n<td height=\"76\"><strong>Charity Navigator :: @</strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/CharityNav\">CharityNav</a><br />\nCharity Reviews, Philanthropy, Research<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.charitynavigator.org/\">charitynavigator.org</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr valign=\"top\">\n<td height=\"76\"><strong>6.</strong></td>\n<td colspan=\"5\" align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" height=\"76\">\n<div><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.diosacommunications.com/nonprofitresources/ChronicleOfPhilanthropy.png?resize=73%2C73\" width=\"73\" height=\"73\" border=\"1\" /></div>\n</td>\n<td height=\"76\"><strong>Chronicle of Philanthropy :: @</strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/philanthropy\">Philanthropy</a><br />\nNews, Research, Jobs<br />\n<a href=\"http://philanthropy.com\">philanthropy.com</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr valign=\"top\">\n<td height=\"76\"><strong>7.</strong></td>\n<td colspan=\"5\" align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" height=\"76\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.diosacommunications.com/nonprofitresources/connectingup.png?resize=73%2C73\" width=\"73\" height=\"73\" border=\"1\" /></td>\n<td height=\"76\"><strong>Connecting Up :: @</strong><a href=\"http://www.connectingup.org/\">ConnectingUp</a><a href=\"http://ext337.org/\"><br />\n</a>Nonprofit Technology, News, Training, Australia<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.connectingup.org/\">connectingup.org</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr valign=\"top\">\n<td height=\"76\"><strong>8.</strong></td>\n<td colspan=\"5\" align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" height=\"76\">\n<div><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.diosacommunications.com/nonprofitresources/Council%20on%20Foundations.jpg?resize=73%2C73\" width=\"73\" height=\"73\" border=\"1\" /></div>\n</td>\n<td height=\"76\"><strong>Council on Foundations :: @</strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/cof_\">COF</a><br />\nPhilanthropy, News, Research<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cof.org/\">cof.org</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr valign=\"top\">\n<td height=\"76\"><strong>9.</strong></td>\n<td colspan=\"5\" align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" height=\"76\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.diosacommunications.com/nonprofitresources/foundationcenter.jpg?resize=73%2C73\" width=\"73\" height=\"73\" border=\"1\" /></td>\n<td height=\"76\"><strong>Foundation Center :: @</strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/fdncenter\">fdncenter</a><br />\nGrants Directory, Philanthropy, Research<br />\n<a href=\"http://foundationcenter.org/\">foundationcenter.org</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr valign=\"top\">\n<td height=\"76\"><strong>10.</strong></td>\n<td colspan=\"5\" align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" height=\"76\">\n<div><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.diosacommunications.com/nonprofitresources/Good.png?resize=73%2C73\" width=\"73\" height=\"73\" border=\"1\" /></div>\n</td>\n<td height=\"76\"><strong>GOOD :: @</strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/good\">GOOD</a><br />\nSocial Good, News<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.good.is\">good.is</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr valign=\"top\">\n<td height=\"76\"><strong>11.</strong></td>\n<td colspan=\"5\" align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" height=\"76\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.diosacommunications.com/nonprofitresources/Guidestar.jpeg?resize=73%2C73\" width=\"73\" height=\"73\" border=\"1\" /></td>\n<td height=\"76\"><strong>GuideStar :: @</strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/guidestarusa\">GuideStarUSA</a><br />\nCharity Ratings, Philanthropy, Research<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.guidestar.org/rxg/products/index.aspx\">guidestar.org</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr valign=\"top\">\n<td height=\"76\"><strong>12.</strong></td>\n<td colspan=\"5\" align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" height=\"76\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.diosacommunications.com/nonprofitresources/HuffingtonPostImapct.png?resize=73%2C73\" width=\"73\" height=\"73\" border=\"1\" /></td>\n<td height=\"76\"><strong>Huffington Post Impact :: @</strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/HuffPostImpact\">HuffPostImpact</a><br />\nSocial Good, News<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.huffingtonpost.com/impact/\">huffingtonpost.com/impact</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr valign=\"top\">\n<td height=\"76\"><strong>13.</strong></td>\n<td colspan=\"5\" align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" height=\"76\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.diosacommunications.com/nonprofitresources/Idealist.jpg?resize=73%2C73\" width=\"73\" height=\"73\" border=\"1\" /></td>\n<td height=\"76\"><strong>Idealist :: @</strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/idealist\">Idealist</a><br />\nJobs, Volunteerism, News<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.idealist.org/\">idealist.org</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr valign=\"top\">\n<td height=\"76\"><strong>14.</strong></td>\n<td colspan=\"5\" align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" height=\"76\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.diosacommunications.com/nonprofitresources/IndependentSector.jpg?resize=73%2C73\" width=\"73\" height=\"73\" border=\"1\" /></td>\n<td height=\"76\"><strong>Independent Sector :: @</strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/indsector\">IndSector</a><br />\nPolicy, Leadership, Governance<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.independentsector.org/\">independentsector.org</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr valign=\"top\">\n<td height=\"76\"><strong>15.</strong></td>\n<td colspan=\"5\" align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" height=\"76\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.diosacommunications.com/nonprofitresources/MashableSocialGood.png?resize=73%2C73\" width=\"73\" height=\"73\" border=\"1\" /></td>\n<td height=\"76\"><strong>Mashable Social Good :: @</strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/socialgood\">SocialGood</a><br />\nSocial Good, Nonprofit Technology<br />\n<a href=\"